Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.84,0:00:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為集齊了5位部員 請批准歌牌部開始正式活動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.70,0:00:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.34,0:00:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.39,0:00:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是部長必須改成綾瀨同學以外的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顧問暫時由我來擔任
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.31,0:00:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 解散
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我就不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 也許是明智的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 部長怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真島就好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸 我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:00:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那我來擔任隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.72,0:00:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部費三千日圓？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買了歌牌之後就一點不剩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起練習方法 我們怎麼進行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先我和真島交換著做綾瀨的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空閒的那個就教小奏和桌子君怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫勉 肉包君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}<桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}肉包>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為千早已經是A級了 \N就和其他兩人實行不同的訓練方式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 A級有那麼厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初從E級開始 在大會中優勝之後升級
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶一說 我和西田是B級
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然根據所屬的歌牌會會有所不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要升A級一般必須在大會中優勝或者獲得2次準優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸？是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！今天要和小奏和桌子君對戰咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要跟駒野和大江同學比賽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說些什麼呀 就算和A級的你進行比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也根本成不了初心者的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們2個也不會覺得有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為部長和隊長哪個更厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸？到底是誰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\be3\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(750,80)\frz270\fn@方正大标宋_GBK\fad(300,600)}第九首
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\be3\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(650,240)\fn@MHGHagoromoTHK-Medium\frz270\fad(300,600)}欲掩不從心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いまをはるべと　さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今兮春滿地 花開香芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いまをはるべと　さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今兮春滿地 花開香芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}おとにきく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高師海浪美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ゆふされば
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮色門前降
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 毫不留情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}あしのまろやに あきかぜぞふく
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖鳴稻葉 蘆舍臨秋風
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}さびしさに
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞門前立
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 果然還是不行 實力差太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小奏 我第一次玩歌牌的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手也是一個超級厲害的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他放水的話我就不會變得那麼喜歡歌牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也不會放水 以全力來進行比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望大家變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:05:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在暑假以我們五人打入團體賽的全國大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近江神宮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是近江神宮？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定日本高中生歌牌第一的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年的4月 在滋賀縣的近江神宮裡舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也被稱作歌牌的甲子園
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是在東京預賽裡取得優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就是全國大賽了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優勝 全國大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 會有多少學校來參加東京預賽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為東京是激戰區啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不可能的 進全國大賽什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們才剛剛起步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.80,0:05:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的 我每天都會全力的做桌子君和小奏的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們可要做好覺悟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸 你指的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是做駒野和大江同學的對手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己就不能練習了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事的話沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼沒問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是以個人戰優勝為目標嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社團你就別管了 去白波會練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和西田會做他們兩人的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們和新三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次參加比賽的事情還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那個時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟大家組成團隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是定位置
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定位置？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 就是事先決定好的自陣的配置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次比賽的時候 我們不可能將牌的位置百分百的記下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經大致決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將喜歡的牌重點擺在右下段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像大江同學那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將「はるす」和「はるの」擺在一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然自己很容易搶到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是對手也是很容易搶到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是說這麼做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你的直覺比對方要好的話是可以搶到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何才能讓自己容易的搶到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何才能使對方很難搶到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習上幾百次後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將只屬於自己的配置用身體牢牢的記住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先最重要的是經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來比賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是左撇子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.57,0:07:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可以把自己喜歡的牌放在左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼簡單可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大山牌當中有理論嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有16張之多的「あ」的牌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請教教我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加天衣無縫的配置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:08:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想輸給後面進來的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}なほあまりある むかしなりけり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁華思舊歲 切切斷人腸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}はなさそふ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿院非白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}しらつゆに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清秋原野上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いにしへの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.95,0:08:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古都奈良城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}わがいほは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我住皇都外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}みよしのの やまのあきかぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故國秋風起 蕭蕭吉野山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 空牌 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗也是一種經驗啊經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}おほえやま
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山長平野闊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶…搶到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次搶到的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下過決心 今天一定要搶到這張牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.67,0:09:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 好厲害啊 哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 我終於也有同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新給我的東西在漸漸擴散哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離校時間早就過了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點給我回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 練習時間根本不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上完課之後只能比賽2場左右
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說根本就不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是沒法鍛煉耐力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到參加比賽的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天要比賽4場以上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 在白波會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的時候 會在河口湖舉行2晚左右的合宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來那個是為了鍛煉耐力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好啊 合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也來辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下週的週六週日因為是創校紀念 所以連休哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:09:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在哪裡辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能留宿又能練習歌牌的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離比賽還有三週
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考慮到尋找場地浪費的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不如練習一場比賽比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把午休和放學時間有效的利用起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少也會起點作用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 附近能夠讓大家都留宿的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那麼簡單能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.21,0:10:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太幸運了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一的父母去神戶參加婚禮去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創校紀念日和星期日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以一整天玩歌牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以使用和室 棉被也夠你們幾個人蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真的連千早也要留下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是隊長嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大家來之前 讓我參觀一下太一的房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我們不是經常一起玩電玩的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家裡人不是又給你買了大電視嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看 讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人的房間不是隨便能進的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不會讓你進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真島…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出生以來第一次感受到貧富差距…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 那樣東西買來了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過合宿感覺讓人心跳不已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有試膽會嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不錯耶 附近會有墓地嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些全部都是真島的?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英語準1級 小提琴 騎馬 滑雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 因為父母喜歡讓我學這學那…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 千早那傢伙竟然把這種多餘的東西給人看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 這位是真島的媽媽?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美麗的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是我不擅長應付她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼沒贏得第一的話就會被她罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稱呼她壓力夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是來練習的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在我宣佈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞澤高中歌牌部第一回合宿的目標是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在今天和明天這兩天內比15場比賽!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對戰表我都做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千 千早 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼都是我和桌子君在比啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 現在最重要的是實戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一場比賽都要集中精神去比哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小奏 你的手揮得太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才教你的姿勢 沒有做到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桌子君 那裡要用按的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神再集中一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你們能變強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想讓你們贏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想讓你們贏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就只有好好練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看 接著是桌子君對肉包君 小奏對…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天先到這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊 才比了五場比賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ながらへば またこのごろや しのばれむ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若得人長在 今朝亦留痕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.97,0:14:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}うしとみしよぞ いまはこひしき
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.97,0:14:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往事雖悲苦 件件可追尋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果人能一直長存的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受到痛苦的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會成為令人懷念的追憶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩人已經到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是到了比賽的時候 就會有許多難受的情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以必須繼續練習才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想累垮拼命努力的人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.11,0:14:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之今天先到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸虧真島是部長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個還不吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有食慾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不吃的話就堅持不下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桌子君 努力吃去下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也需要練習的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桌子君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小奏 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了 快躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀太一 你朋友來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天不是在那邊過夜嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪梨香突然說想要回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}USJ：Universal Studios Japan的縮寫 \N是位於大阪市的好萊塢電影主題公園 2001年開設
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不去USJ 就沒有任何意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}梨香真是任性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真危險啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繞到玄關拿回鞋子 然後到我家去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓力夫人是不可能答應讓女孩子留下來過夜的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想累垮拼命努力的人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說我經常被人說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「千早眼中只有花牌」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒用…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下 小奏?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小奏?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三更半夜 要去哪裡啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 我說小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 要跑到哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～　千早 這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一? 大家也在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉在這種時候叫你過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們今晚無論如何也有話想跟隊長說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.26,0:17:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我先說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 完全沒有看到周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得大家都在努力了 我還勉強大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦 綾瀨這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強硬是綾瀨的性格 有一個這樣的人在也挺不錯的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為有對歌牌專心一志的千早在…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家才會想要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還有很多不懂的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我好像也會喜歡上歌牌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桌子君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 快點吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在真島媽媽洗完澡之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 忘了拿刀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這是調羹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 就這麼吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.46,0:18:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣 太沒禮貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 千早巧克力塊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點吃快點吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這黃色的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的份
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早也快點來吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你笑了 歌牌才會有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的哦 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡蛋糕的皮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.67,0:19:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能把一圈都吃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是千早的生日 當然可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真島的媽媽還真是有點可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰去給浴室上個鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.98,0:19:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.92,0:19:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陌生地址
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把最後一口蛋糕皮給你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 才不給你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真島的媽媽真的很可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.89,0:20:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 流星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次看見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:21:00.34,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正准圆_GBK}{\fs26}{\1a&H6E&\1c&H704338&}{\be1}{\frz7}{\pos(300,280)\fad(200,600)\bord0}太一 之前抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:21:00.34,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正准圆_GBK}{\fs26}{\1a&H6E&\1c&H704338&}{\be1}{\frz7}{\pos(320,310)\bord0\fad(200,600)}替我向千早說聲生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.74,0:20:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16歲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.15,0:21:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我過的最好的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡 在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:11.44,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}帰り道は過ぎていく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:14.82,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}少し風が吹いている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:19.99,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}たわいない会話妙に楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:24.87,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今でも変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:28.61,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}僕ら待ち合わせたあの場所
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.83,0:01:33.98,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君はまだ覚えてるのかな?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.10,0:01:41.82,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今はちはやふる想い胸に抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:47.16,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}目指した先に何があるんだ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.26,0:01:52.94,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今なら掴めそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:55.82,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}手を伸ばしてみる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:02:02.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}夢の途中きっといつかまた会えるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:11.44,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}慢步走過回家的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:14.82,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}微風輕輕吹拂著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:19.99,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}閒話家常也異常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:24.87,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}至今依舊一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:28.61,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}我們常常相約等候的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.83,0:01:33.98,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}你可否仍然記得呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.10,0:01:41.82,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}現在我心懷強烈的嚮往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.94,0:01:47.16,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}有什麼在目標之處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.26,0:01:52.94,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}現在的話似乎能抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:55.82,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}試著伸出雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:02:02.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}在夢想的路上終有一天會再度重逢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:29.61,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま ふたりは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:34.52,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}遠すぎる世界見つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:40.07,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま ほら 響くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:47.35,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君が教えてくれた歌 この空で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:52.48,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま わたしは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:57.48,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君に続く空見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:22:02.90,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま まだ歌うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:07.65,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}どこにいたって届くはずだって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:12.83,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま ふたりは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:17.88,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}輝く明日を見つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:23.36,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}そしていま ほら 響くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.54,0:22:31.77,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君が教えてくれた歌 この空に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:29.61,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}於是此刻你我兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:34.52,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}凝望著遙不可及的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:40.07,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}於是此刻 你聽 歌聲響徹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:47.35,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}你曾經教會我唱的歌謠  迴響在這片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:52.48,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}於是此刻 我舉頭仰望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:57.48,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}延伸到你身旁的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:22:02.90,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}於是此刻 依然歌唱著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:07.65,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}無論身處何方也應該傳遞得到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:12.83,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}於是此刻你我兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:17.88,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}凝望著光輝閃爍的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:23.36,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}於是此刻 你聽 歌聲響徹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.54,0:22:31.77,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}你曾經教會我唱的歌謠 迴響於這片天空
